# Product Rules

## Product Identity
This product is a mobile-first Household Financial Operating System.

It is a shared household budgeting and expense management system.

It is not:
- a generic personal expense tracker
- an accounting tool
- bookkeeping software
- an invoicing tool
- a banking app

The product is household-first, not user-first.

All financial records belong to a household.

Users participate in a household through role-based membership.

This rule is non-negotiable.

---

## MVP Scope
MVP includes only:

- authentication
- household management
- membership
- monthly budgets
- budget categories
- budget adjustments
- budget reallocations
- transactions
- quick add expense
- recurring expenses
- attachments
- dashboard
- forecasting
- monthly insights
- monthly close
- Bengali + English localization
- audit logs

Do not add beyond this scope unless explicitly instructed.

---

## Explicitly Out of Scope
Do not add:

- income tracking
- wallet/account tracking
- bank sync
- card sync
- debt tracking
- lending tracker
- installment tracking
- investments
- savings goals
- AI receipt parsing
- AI voice input
- AI expense parsing
- AI suggestions
- AI coaching
- tax/accounting workflows
- invoicing
- bookkeeping

These are not MVP features.

Do not implement them unless explicitly instructed.

---

## Product Rules
- Household-first always
- Mobile-first always
- Expense-first workflow
- Fast expense logging is critical
- Budgeting must remain flexible
- Financial changes must be auditable
- Closed months are read-only
- AI is optional and not part of MVP
- App must work without AI